Mutane sama da miliyan 20 sun kalli shaidar mai ban sha'awa a kan tashoshin talabijin shida a ranar Alhamis na dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh da Kirista Blasey Ford, matar da ta tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin da ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, matsalar siyasa ta ci gaba, tare da masu watsa shirye-shirye suna katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullun don juyin juya halin ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya samu don FBI ta gudanar da binciken mako guda.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai cewa ta tabbata kashi 100 bisa 100 cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade cikin maye kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta a wani biki na makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da ya bayar da himma, ya ce ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli bidiyon a ranar Jumma'a, in ji Nielsen.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin kallon CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu lambobin nan da nan ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna shi ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma wani lokaci Nielsen yana da wuya ya auna yawan mutanen da suke kallon ofisoshin.
Don sanya shi cikin hangen nesa, wannan shine girman masu sauraro kamar na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko na kyautar Academy.
Fox News Channel, wanda masu sauraronsa suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ya kasance a gaban dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin sauraron ranar, Nielsen ya ce.
ABC ta kasance ta biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1, NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94, MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2.89 kuma CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52, Nielsen ya ce.
Har ila, mutane suna son su saurari wannan jawabin.
Flake ne ainihin mutumin da ke cikin wasan kwaikwayon Jumma'a.
Bayan da ofishin 'yan Republican masu matsakaicin matsayi suka ba da sanarwar cewa za su kada kuri'ar Kavanaugh, an kama shi a CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a inda masu zanga-zanga ke ihu a kansa yayin da yake kokarin daukar lif zuwa Kwamitin Shari'a.
Ya tsaya na 'yan mintoci kaɗan yana kallon CNN da ido a ƙasa yana kallon yadda ake yi masa baƙar magana.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
