Lokacin taron Trump na West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zaben a Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin gangamin Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake a halin yanzu ana riƙe da kuri'ar tabbatarwa don zaɓin sa don cike gurbin da ke gaban kotun kolin, Trump yana son gina goyon baya don zaben da ke tafe saboda 'yan Republican na cikin haɗarin rasa iko a kan Majalisar lokacin da aka kada kuri'a a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a yammacin Virginia a yau da dare kuma ta yaya za a kalli taron a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a karfe 7 na yamma ET a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a yammacin Virginia ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye a ƙasa.
Trump zai iya mayar da hankali kan sauraron shari'ar wannan makon ga wanda aka zaba a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya damu game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i tare da zabar kuri'ar tabbatarwa da aka yi a cikin mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban manufar wannan taron shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba.
A sakamakon haka, kamfen ɗin Shugaba Trump ya ce waɗannan tarurruka biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa za su kasance ne don "su ziyarci masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin kāre da kuma ƙara rinjaye da suke da shi a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa, don haka shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai yiwu lokacin da muke shiga lokacin kamfen", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya ki a bayyana sunansa, ya shaida wa Reuters.
An shirya taron na daren nan a filin wasa na Westbanco da ke Wheeling, kuma za a iya samun magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a iya samun rahoto daga kafofin yaɗa labarai a Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a sakamakon zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi goyon baya a ma'aikatar zabe", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
