Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya soki mutumci mai guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin HBO mai ban tsoro na zamani na wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones.
Amma, ɗan wasan, mai shekara 31, ya yi sūkar ra'ayin jarumi mai son kai, ya ce irin wannan aikin a kan allon yana nufin cewa yara maza suna yawan jin cewa dole ne su yi ƙoƙari su zama masu daraja.
Kit ya yi magana da The Sunday Times Culture, yana mai cewa ya yi imanin "wani abu ya tafi ba daidai ba" kuma ya tambayi yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa a zamanin #MeToo.
