a cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai shiga cikin kowane wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones ba da kuma abubuwan da suka faru a lokacin da jerin suka ƙare a bazara na gaba, saboda ya ce ya "ƙare da fagen fama da dawakai".
