HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta Rarraba Sabbin Cutar HIV da Ta Kamu da Ita da Kashi 14
China ta sanar da cewa akwai ƙaruwa da kashi 14% cikin yawan 'yan ƙasa da ke rayuwa da HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 a ƙasar sun kamu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
Kimanin sabbin mutane 40,000 aka bayar da rahoton su a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka suna faruwa ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa da sauri a wasu ɓangarorin ƙasar Sin ta wajen karɓan ƙarin jini daga waɗanda suka kamu da ita.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na ƙasar Sin a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Shekara bayan shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i lamari ne mai matukar muhimmanci a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT.
Domin ɗabi'ar da ta dace a ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke kwana da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna zuwa daga rashin kāriya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun maganin HIV ga kowa a kasar a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
