Amurka na iya amfani da jiragen ruwa don "kulle" don dakatar da fitar da makamashin Rasha - ministan cikin gida
"Idan ya cancanta", Washington za ta iya dogara da rundunar jiragen ruwa don hana makamashi na Rasha shiga kasuwa, ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya nakalto.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar Rasha cikin Syria - musamman ma inda take aiki a gayyatar da gwamnatin da ta dace - wata hujja ce ta bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Na yi imani dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son su zama dillalan makamashi kamar yadda suke a Gabashin Turai, Kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma, a cewar wani jami'in, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin magance wannan.
"Amurka tana da ikon, tare da Sojojin Ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin teku suna buɗe, kuma idan ya cancanta, don toshewa, don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba ya shiga kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi jawabi ga masu halarta a wani taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta wacce ke daukar kanta a matsayin "muryar mai amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta hanyoyin da Washington ke bi wajen magance Rasha da Iran, ya lura cewa sun yi kama da juna.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki ga Iran da Rasha shine, a mafi yawancin, don tallafawa da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yana mai cewa Rasha "ƙwararren mutum ne" tare da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da burbushin mai.
Wannan hukunci ya zo ne a yayin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan aikin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai domin maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ta fi karfin masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Saboda haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, sun yi kokarin lallashe Jamus ta janye daga aikin bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 wanda ba daidai ba, wanda Trump ya ce ya sa Berlin ta zama " fursuna " ga Moscow.
Moscow ta maimaita cewa aikin famfo mai daraja dala biliyan 11, wanda zai ninka karfin famfo na yanzu zuwa biliyan 110 na cubic mita, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa Washington ta nuna adawa da aikin ne kawai saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na gasa mara kyau.
"Na yi imani muna da ra'ayin cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama hanyar matsa lamba ba kuma masu amfani da shi su zaɓi masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amirka, Rick Perry, a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Ra'ayin Amurka ya haifar da rashin amincewa daga Jamus, wanda ya sake tabbatar da alƙawarinsa ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Tarayyar Masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI) ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta nisanta kanta daga manufofin makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da ya yi da shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da kuma shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta "tunani sosai" game da neman shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020, in ji Sanatan Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta "tunani sosai" kan neman shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron gari a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi la'akari da tsayawa takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace kuma hakan ya hada da mace a manyan wasanni", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan Nuwamba 6, zan yi tunani sosai game da neman shugaban kasa".
Warren ta bayyana ra'ayinta game da Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin taron gari, yana cewa yana "karkatar da kasar zuwa hanya mara kyau.
"Ina cikin damuwa game da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ta kasance mai matukar adawa da Trump da kuma nadin Brett Kavanaugh a Kotun Koli.
A wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce "ba shakka muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin mu kada kuri'a".
Wani binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'ar Warren ba sa ganin ya kamata ta tsaya takara a 2020.
Fiye da kashi hamsin da takwas na masu zaɓen Massachusetts da "suna iya" cewa ba za su tsaya ba, in ji binciken Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da Boston Globe.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari sun goyi bayan ra'ayin cewa ta kamata ta tsaya.
