Za a iya "daure wani mako" don ganawar Donald Trump da mataimakin babban lauyan kasar Rod Rosenstein yayin da ake ci gaba da fada kan wanda zai zama babban alkalin kotun kolin kasar, Brett Kavanaugh, fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein ya kula da aikin mai ba da shawara kan shari'a na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken shigar da baki a zaben Rasha, alaƙar da ke tsakanin masu taimaka wa Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban yin aiki da doka.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauyan kasar ko a'a, kuma hakan ya yi barazana ga 'yancin Mueller, ya kasance yana ta janyo jita-jita a Washington har tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna batun sanya na'urar daukar sauti don rikodin tattaunawa da Trump, da kuma yiwuwar cire shugaban ta hanyar Amincewa ta 25.
