Trump ya ce zai "fi son kada" ya yi murabus daga Rosenstein, amma sai aka dage taron don kauce wa gwagwarmayar da kotun majalisa ta yi da Kavanaugh da kuma wata mata da ta zarge shi da lalata, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, duka sun shaida.
