Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Aƙalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da tsunami da ta auku a birnin Palu na ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Jumma'a, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai ƙaru.
Da aka kashe sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu kusa da cibiyar girgizar ƙasa mai girman 7.5.
A Palu, an kai mutane fiye da 16,000 wurin da babu haɗari bayan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke kan iyakar wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardi, a cikin 2017 an kiyasta yawan jama'arta 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune ginshikan tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana zaune a kan Ringin Wuta na Tekun Fasifik kuma yawan girgizar ƙasa tana faruwa a wurin.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu, an yi wata guguwa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girman 6.8 ya afku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a Indonesia, wanda ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya afku a gabar kudu kuma ya yi sanadin mutuwar kusan mutane 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa gwamnatin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da halakar girgizar kasa da tsunami mai kisa a 2004.
Wannan ba tsunami ba ne, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu saboda gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda mutane sama da 500 suka mutu, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a makale.
