Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba saboda wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, an yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a gefen hanyar West Side a Lower Manhattan don kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da kuma mai hawan keke a cikin hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "da gangan" ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma ya yi mummunan rauni ga jiki, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka shigar a Kudancin Gundumar New York.
An ce duka waɗannan tuhume-tuhume suna da hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke hukuncin kisa Saipov kan laifuka 22, wanda ya hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai don neman kudi, wanda ake amfani da shi a cikin masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a cikin al'amuran da suka shafi al'ada, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da ƙara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi da kyau da kuma yin tunani sosai", kuma sun kwatanta yadda Saipov ya yi shi da "mummunan hali, mugunta, da kuma lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asarar dangi da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar niyyar.
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe masu yawon buɗe ido ne daga ƙasar Ajantina.
Shekara goma ta shige tun lokacin da gundumar New York ta Kudu ta fara shari'ar kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekara ta 1953 ne aka yi kisa a sabuwar shari'a da aka yi a New York, an kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa bayan an yanke musu hukuncin yin leƙen asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe Rosenberges biyu da kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu wahayi don kai harin bayan kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
