An ɗauki wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a ƙasar Indonesia a matsayin gwarzo bayan ya mutu don ya tabbata cewa jirgin da ke ɗauke da ɗarurruwan mutane ya tashi lafiya.
Mutane sama da 800 ne suka mutu, wasu kuma sun bace bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da tsunami.
Har ila, ana ci gaba da fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun faɗa cikin tarkace a birnin Palu.
