Raƙuman ruwa da suka kai kafa shida sun halaka birnin Palu da za a yi jana'izar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna kawo taimako da kayayyaki.
Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiya 'yar shekara 35, ta gaya wa Sky News: "Kowane minti motar asibiti tana kawo gawarwaki.
