Shugabar 'yan majalisa Nancy Pelosi ta kira dan majalisar dattijai Brett Kavanaugh "rashin hankali" kuma ta ce ba shi da cancantar yin aiki a kotun koli.
Pelosi ta yi wannan jawabin ne a wata hira da ta yi da shi a Texas Tribune Festival da ke Austin, Texas a ranar Asabar.
"Ba zan iya guje wa tunanin cewa idan wata mace ta taɓa yin hakan ba, za su ce 'rashin hankali,'" in ji Pelosi game da yadda ta amsa shaidar Kavanaugh a gaban kwamitin shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa a ranar Alhamis.
Kavanaugh ya musanta zargin cewa ya yi lalata da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford lokacin da suke matashi.
A lokacin jawabinsa na farko, Kavanaugh ya kasance mai matukar damuwa, a wasu lokutan yana kusan ihu da kuma nutsuwa yayin da yake tattauna danginsa da shekarun makarantar sakandarensa.
Ya kuma nuna rashin amincewarsa ga 'yan Democrat a kwamitin, yana mai cewa zargin da ake yi masa "abin dariya ne kuma an shirya kisan gilla ne", wanda 'yan liberal suka shirya saboda rashin jin daɗin Hillary Clinton a zaben shugaban kasa na 2016.
Pelosi ta ce ta yi imanin shaidar Kavanaugh ta tabbatar da cewa ba zai iya zama a Kotun Koli ba saboda ya nuna cewa yana da nuna bambanci ga 'yan Democrat.
"Ina ganin yana nuna rashin cancanta ne da wadannan maganganun da kuma yadda ya bi bayan Clinton da 'yan Democrat", in ji ta.
Pelosi ta yi jinkirin lokacin da aka tambaye ta ko za ta yi kokarin tuhumar Kavanaugh idan aka tabbatar da shi, kuma idan 'yan Democrat suka sami rinjaye a majalisar wakilai.
"Zan ce wannan - idan bai gaya wa Majalisa ko FBI gaskiya ba, to ba shi da ikon zama a Kotun Koli, amma ya kasance a kotun da yake yanzu", in ji Pelosi.
Kavanaugh a halin yanzu shi ne alƙali a Kotun daukaka ƙara ta D.C.
Pelosi ta kara da cewa a matsayinta na Democrat, ta damu da yiwuwar yanke hukuncin Kavanaugh game da Dokar Kula da Lafiya ko Roe v. Wade saboda ana ganin shi mai kiyaye doka ne.
A lokacin da ake sauraron karar, Kavanaugh ya yi watsi da tambayoyi game da ko zai soke wasu hukuncin Kotun Koli.
"Wannan ba lokacin da wani mai tsattsauran ra'ayi zai je kotu ya ce, 'Ba abin mamaki ba ne?' " in ji Pelosi.
