Yadda Yakin Ciniki na Amurka da China Zai Iya Amfanar Beijing
Tun da yake an fara yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China da sauti mai ban tsoro, kuma yayin da yakin ya yi nisa da ƙarshe, ƙwararru sun ce rashin jituwa tsakanin ƙasashen na iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara gargadi a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da China ke fitarwa, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminium.
Mafi girman tashin hankali ya fara ne a wannan makon tare da sabbin haraji da suka shafi abubuwa tiriliyan $200 (£150 tiriliyan) kuma a zahiri suna sanya haraji kan rabin kayan da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta yi ramako a kan kayayyaki a kowane lokaci, kuma kwanan nan ta saka haraji tsakanin kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa ɗari a kan kayayyakin Amirka da suka kai dala tiriliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta yi daidai da Amurka harbi-harbi, kuma babbar tattalin arzikin duniya ba za ta yi wani abu ba.
Don samun Washington ta yi baya yana nufin mika wuya ga buƙatun, amma yin biyayya ga buƙatun Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban China.
Masana sun ci gaba da cewa idan Beijing ta yi wasa da katunan ta yadda ya kamata, matsin lamba kan yakin cinikayya na Amurka a kan dogon lokaci na iya tallafawa China ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
Gaskiyar cewa yanke shawara na siyasa cikin sauri a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai iya haifar da tashin hankali na tattalin arziki a kowace ƙasa, hakika ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu kallo suka riga suka yarda, "in ji Abigail Grace, mataimakiyar bincike mai mayar da hankali kan Asiya a tsakiyar New American Security, mai tunani.
